## Preamble

```bash
# ---- Session Tracking ----
mkdir -p ~/.{{PROJECT_NAME}}/sessions
touch ~/.{{PROJECT_NAME}}/sessions/"$PPID"
_SESSIONS=$(find ~/.{{PROJECT_NAME}}/sessions -mmin -120 -type f 2>/dev/null | wc -l | tr -d ' ')

# ---- Branch Detection ----
_BRANCH=$(git branch --show-current 2>/dev/null || echo "unknown")
_BASE=$(git remote show origin 2>/dev/null | grep 'HEAD branch' | awk '{print $NF}' || echo "main")

# ---- Config Loading ----
_PROACTIVE=$(cat ~/.{{PROJECT_NAME}}/config/proactive 2>/dev/null || echo "true")

# ---- Output ----
echo "SKILL: {{SKILL_NAME}}"
echo "BRANCH: $_BRANCH"
echo "BASE: $_BASE"
echo "SESSIONS: $_SESSIONS"
echo "PROACTIVE: $_PROACTIVE"
```

Read the output above. Store BRANCH, BASE, SESSIONS, and PROACTIVE as context for this session.

